data.description: Gorgeous house ready for your buyer to make this their home! This house has a generous space with plenty of room to spread out and grow. Spacious bedrooms with space to study, relax, sleep and plenty of storage. The kitchen is open to the family room which features a fireplace and has a beautiful sunroom attached to the family room. Off of the sunroom is a spacious deck and backyard. The owners suite is complete with a fireplace, walk-in closet, sitting area with a bathroom that features a separate garden tub and shower. Your buyer will receive great enjoyment in the full finished basement that includes a full bedroom, bathroom, and sitting area. The basement also includes other multifunctional rooms to be used however desired. Bring your buyers, this one won't last long!
